-- Bharat Petroleum Is in Talks to Buy Shell's Retail Fuel Outlets in India
-- Rakteem Katakey
-- 2010-07-13T05:32:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/bharat-petroleum-is-in-talks-to-buy-shell-s-retail-fuel-outlets-in-india.html

          
          
             Bharat Petroleum Corp. is in talks
to buy about 20 of Royal Dutch Shell Plc’s retail fuel outlets
in India, an official of the Indian refiner said, asking not to
be identified because he’s not allowed to speak to the media.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Rakteem Katakey in New Delhi at 
 rkatakey@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        